  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the changes in cognitive function after miglustat treatment in Niemann-Pick type
      C patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients with Niemann-Pick C disease will be treated with Miglutat 200mg tid. Neurologic
      evaluation and safety will be monitored periodically.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
